<sentence>　貝を空から<event class="" eid="e4">落とし</event>て<event class="" eid="e5">割っ</event>たり、クルミを車に<event class="" eid="e6">ひかせ</event>たり<event class="" eid="e7">し</event>て<event class="" eid="e8">食べる</event>。</sentence>
